1
00:00:01,040 --> 00:00:09,300
After the great tour of UK I feel very confident that Sahaja Yoga

2
00:00:09,380 --> 00:00:14,030
is taking its roots, and you can see some of the plants coming up.

3
00:00:14,424 --> 00:00:18,490
It’s surprising, when I declared that it may be the last tour

4
00:00:18,570 --> 00:00:22,650
I’ll be doing of UK that things have started working out.

5
00:00:23,000 --> 00:00:27,760
Everywhere we went it was very good and successful,

6
00:00:28,000 --> 00:00:31,720
specially certain places it was very miraculous.

7
00:00:31,800 --> 00:00:36,820
You must have heard about the lady who would not go out of her house,

8
00:00:36,900 --> 00:00:38,966
was suffering from agoraphobia,

9
00:00:39,890 --> 00:00:43,230
and the press challenged us that she should be

10
00:00:43,310 --> 00:00:45,750
cured because she can’t go out of the house.

11
00:00:45,830 --> 00:00:50,570
And only on her photograph and treatment she got cured, and now she’s walking about,

12
00:00:50,650 --> 00:00:56,830
and they have given a big report saying that ‘The Guru fulfills Her promise’.

13
00:00:58,034 --> 00:01:02,900
This is one of them and there are many things have happened of this kind,

14
00:01:02,980 --> 00:01:05,313
of which you should get the report.

15
00:01:05,760 --> 00:01:09,560
I must say I found all the sahaja yogis very cooperative,

16
00:01:09,640 --> 00:01:16,880
very alert, very helpful and extremely progressive.

17
00:01:18,160 --> 00:01:23,250
And I was happy that they are trying to come up and improve themselves,

18
00:01:23,330 --> 00:01:30,240
build themselves up, and are doing much better than what I had expected, really.

19
00:01:30,320 --> 00:01:35,100
I was very, very enamored by all of them, and I hope that by the time it

20
00:01:35,180 --> 00:01:43,100
is 12 years, we’ll be all absolutely top class sahaja yogis of the world.

21
00:01:43,180 --> 00:01:46,440
Now today is a very great day of Raksha Bandhan,

22
00:01:48,620 --> 00:01:53,760
so I have to tell you something about Raksha Bandhan.

23
00:01:53,840 --> 00:02:11,160
Before that we have to talk about the maryadas

24
00:02:12,880 --> 00:02:16,870
that are to be observed by sahaja yogis.

25
00:02:20,680 --> 00:02:26,020
One of the things I discovered here, in the West,

26
00:02:26,100 --> 00:02:31,535
that though we have understood the importance of Mooladhara, which is a very

27
00:02:31,615 --> 00:02:36,320
important thing and that unless and until we re-establish our

28
00:02:36,400 --> 00:02:42,280
Mooladhara fully we are not going to have a speediest ascent.

29
00:02:42,640 --> 00:02:47,260
Despite all that, still there are lingering things you see around.

30
00:02:48,090 --> 00:02:58,190
Like people start choosing their life partners in Sahaja Yoga.

31
00:02:59,680 --> 00:03:04,300
That is not allowed, that is not allowed.

32
00:03:04,380 --> 00:03:09,640
You are not to spoil your ashrams, your centres,

33
00:03:10,090 --> 00:03:13,970
using them for a marriage searching society.

34
00:03:14,954 --> 00:03:18,220
You must respect it, this point you must respect.

35
00:03:18,300 --> 00:03:21,130
If you have to marry,

36
00:03:21,420 --> 00:03:27,660
then you can find your life partner outside Sahaja Yoga – to begin with.

37
00:03:27,740 --> 00:03:31,280
But if you want to marry in Sahaja Yoga,

38
00:03:31,440 --> 00:03:36,890
then you should not go on searching people in Sahaja Yoga.

39
00:03:36,970 --> 00:03:41,503
Is a very dangerous thing for Sahaja Yoga itself and for you people.

40
00:03:43,340 --> 00:03:47,540
That is one thing one should never try to do with sahaja yogis.

41
00:03:47,620 --> 00:03:51,210
For all practical purposes you are brothers and sisters.

42
00:03:51,290 --> 00:03:55,530
And that’s why I always encourage marriages between

43
00:03:55,610 --> 00:03:59,390
people who belong to another country or another centres.

44
00:04:00,930 --> 00:04:05,420
As we are now having a marriage – big program

45
00:04:07,210 --> 00:04:12,520
– I would say that most of the marriages which

46
00:04:12,600 --> 00:04:15,980
were done like that are very successful than

47
00:04:16,060 --> 00:04:19,193
the marriages that were selected and were done.

48
00:04:19,273 --> 00:04:22,340
It’s very wrong to do such a thing as to arrange

49
00:04:22,420 --> 00:04:25,420
your marriage with a sahaja yogi by yourself.

50
00:04:26,560 --> 00:04:27,960
It will be dangerous.

51
00:04:28,040 --> 00:04:31,220
I don’t want to say anything, but it won’t turn out to be good,

52
00:04:31,300 --> 00:04:35,390
because it is anti-God activity, absolutely anti-God.

53
00:04:35,470 --> 00:04:38,502
You are supposed to develop your brahmacharya,

54
00:04:38,582 --> 00:04:40,805
you are supposed to develop your Mooladhara.

55
00:04:41,070 --> 00:04:46,340
Instead of that, if you start using a sahaja yogini or a sahaja yogi for

56
00:04:46,420 --> 00:04:50,820
the selection of your married life, it’s going to be very, very troublesome.

57
00:04:50,900 --> 00:04:52,840
Your Mooladhara will not settle down.

58
00:04:52,920 --> 00:04:57,020
I mean that’s a very bad stroke for your development.

59
00:04:57,100 --> 00:05:01,920
Because of the background and the kind of conditioning you have had,

60
00:05:02,280 --> 00:05:03,380
you people don’t

61
00:05:03,460 --> 00:05:10,355
understand that it is important to maintain the purity of the centres,

62
00:05:10,435 --> 00:05:16,160
and of every place. So any such relationship in one city is a very wrong thing.

63
00:05:16,340 --> 00:05:17,606
It spoils everyone.

64
00:05:17,686 --> 00:05:23,010
To add up to the trouble, it’s a habit of people, I have heard, that they try to

65
00:05:23,090 --> 00:05:28,230
tease that “You look better together, you are nice together.” They tease and enjoy.

66
00:05:28,310 --> 00:05:36,300
It’s a kind of a very perverted enjoyment of Mooladhara, to tease others “You are

67
00:05:36,380 --> 00:05:37,580
looking very nice with him,

68
00:05:37,660 --> 00:05:41,526
and you better marry.” It’s a kind of a romantic nonsense.

69
00:05:41,606 --> 00:05:45,590
Of course, for all the yogis they have to have a brahmacharya.

70
00:05:45,670 --> 00:05:48,710
But even if you can’t have brahmacharya you must have maryadas.

71
00:05:48,790 --> 00:05:54,650
Not to tease each other and enjoy that kind of a nonsense,

72
00:05:54,730 --> 00:05:57,950
when the marriage is not settled. [If] marriage [is] settled, is all right.

73
00:05:58,030 --> 00:06:02,370
And this kills completely the joy of marriage, because there is no curiosity left.

74
00:06:02,450 --> 00:06:07,270
And many a times I find that absurd relations are established.

75
00:06:07,350 --> 00:06:11,070
Some of them are really no good, and they will really be detrimental,

76
00:06:11,150 --> 00:06:14,690
and some of them never are established.

77
00:06:14,770 --> 00:06:17,340
So if they are established, they are wrong,

78
00:06:17,420 --> 00:06:21,640
and if they are not established, they are heartbreaking.

79
00:06:21,720 --> 00:06:24,620
So all this kind of thing you should not do.

80
00:06:24,700 --> 00:06:26,920
We’ve got experiences of people who married outside

81
00:06:27,000 --> 00:06:30,880
and brought wonderful people to Sahaja Yoga.

82
00:06:30,960 --> 00:06:32,740
If you can do it, you should do it.

83
00:06:32,820 --> 00:06:37,060
But if you have to marry sahaja yogis, you should not marry them

84
00:06:37,140 --> 00:06:41,560
at the cost of destroying the purity and the idealism it has.

85
00:06:42,260 --> 00:06:45,060
For your own sake, for your own pleasures,

86
00:06:45,140 --> 00:06:47,680
you should not spoil the name of Sahaja Yoga.

87
00:06:47,760 --> 00:06:53,040
That is one thing I have seen, so I would say that today, as it is the day of purity

88
00:06:53,120 --> 00:06:54,140
between relationship,

89
00:06:54,220 --> 00:06:59,020
let us know that you have to treat each other as brothers and sisters.

90
00:07:01,100 --> 00:07:03,540
No such play should be followed.

91
00:07:03,620 --> 00:07:05,700
Don’t allow your mind to drift into this.

92
00:07:05,780 --> 00:07:08,480
Because if you allow, then there’s no end to it.

93
00:07:08,560 --> 00:07:12,860
As it is, you know how hard it is to bring you back to normalcy.

94
00:07:16,007 --> 00:07:19,540
When Christ had said, “Thou shalt not have adulterous

95
00:07:19,620 --> 00:07:22,820
eyes,” He didn’t say it because it was not practical.

96
00:07:22,900 --> 00:07:25,500
It is quite practical for sahaja yogis.

97
00:07:25,580 --> 00:07:28,340
And there is nothing to worry about marriages so much.

98
00:07:28,420 --> 00:07:29,560
What is so important?

99
00:07:29,640 --> 00:07:32,470
So many are married and what has happened to them.

100
00:07:32,550 --> 00:07:33,990
Even with Sahaja Yoga marriage,

101
00:07:34,070 --> 00:07:37,390
some of them have failed because of these bad habits.

102
00:07:37,470 --> 00:07:40,170
So you better get rid of these bad habits before marriage,

103
00:07:40,250 --> 00:07:44,930
because after marriage also they go on like this, and searching for boys and girls.

104
00:07:45,010 --> 00:07:48,910
Because if these habits are not curbed before marriage,

105
00:07:48,990 --> 00:07:50,760
then they go on lingering on.

106
00:07:50,840 --> 00:07:54,500
So one should not try to do all these things before marriage.

107
00:07:54,580 --> 00:07:59,160
And I have seen such marriages are never, never successful so far.

108
00:07:59,240 --> 00:08:02,700
And even if they are, it is a sort of a make-believe thing.

109
00:08:02,780 --> 00:08:05,980
It doesn’t give real joy, it’s a joyless pursuit.

110
00:08:06,060 --> 00:08:08,280
Maybe in one case, may be successful;

111
00:08:08,360 --> 00:08:13,020
that doesn’t mean that you should take any help from such difficult

112
00:08:13,100 --> 00:08:15,840
things, but have normal marriages which are enjoyable,

113
00:08:15,920 --> 00:08:21,670
which have created permanent bondages between people.

114
00:08:27,650 --> 00:08:32,983
Now we have to understand the maryadas, about which I have told you before also.

115
00:08:33,250 --> 00:08:37,729
The relationships between men and women are only

116
00:08:37,809 --> 00:08:43,980
pure if a certain amount of boundaries are kept.

117
00:08:44,460 --> 00:08:49,940
Like, supposing you have milk in one container and

118
00:08:50,020 --> 00:08:52,520
you have got something else in another container.

119
00:08:52,600 --> 00:08:58,320
To keep the purity of one container, you have to keep it in its bounds, in the cup.

120
00:08:58,954 --> 00:09:03,420
If you allow them to mix up, if they fall together and they mix up,

121
00:09:03,500 --> 00:09:07,080
then there is no purity left – is a simple thing like that.

122
00:09:07,160 --> 00:09:12,480
One should understand, that we have to understand that how to keep our

123
00:09:12,560 --> 00:09:17,300
relationships in proper respect to each other’s modesty and chastity.

124
00:09:21,270 --> 00:09:26,330
Now for example, there is a girl who is younger to you.

125
00:09:27,580 --> 00:09:30,913
You must keep all the distance from such a person.

126
00:09:31,790 --> 00:09:36,090
If she is much older than you, then it is all right.

127
00:09:36,170 --> 00:09:40,650
You can talk, laugh, joke – she’s much older than you.

128
00:09:40,730 --> 00:09:46,440
But normally with a girl who is younger to you, even much younger, you should try

129
00:09:46,520 --> 00:09:52,300
to keep away, after all if she is a young girl; not with the children, but still.

130
00:09:52,380 --> 00:09:57,195
You must learn these things: how to maintain a distance.

131
00:09:57,275 --> 00:10:00,940
Now, if there’s a man who is younger to you,

132
00:10:02,220 --> 00:10:08,040
then you must not have any funny ideas about such a person – is absolutely absurd.

133
00:10:09,020 --> 00:10:14,420
If some gentleman is younger to you, it’s in, only perversion you do such things.

134
00:10:14,500 --> 00:10:18,240
You see, you should not have any funny ideas about that person.

135
00:10:18,320 --> 00:10:22,800
It’s only done when there are emergencies, when there is no possibility of a

136
00:10:22,880 --> 00:10:24,480
marriage,

137
00:10:24,560 --> 00:10:29,940
when there are so many women or so many men – or under perverted conditions.

138
00:10:30,020 --> 00:10:34,700
We don’t have none of these conditions here, so we have to behave like normal

139
00:10:34,780 --> 00:10:40,020
people, and when the proper atmosphere is given to us, why not make use of it?

140
00:10:40,100 --> 00:10:42,560
Why should we create absurd things?

141
00:10:42,640 --> 00:10:47,775
Then they come out to Me saying that “Mother, now we have decided to marry.

142
00:10:47,855 --> 00:10:51,610
Let us marry.” I have to say “Yes.” [With] many things I don’t want to say “Yes”,

143
00:10:51,690 --> 00:10:53,550
but I have to say “Yes.” But [it] creates a very bad precedent.

144
00:10:53,630 --> 00:10:57,450
Maybe that in certain cases, as an exceptional case,

145
00:10:57,590 --> 00:11:00,790
I might have chosen to marry somebody like that.

146
00:11:00,870 --> 00:11:03,250
But that doesn’t mean you should take things into your hands,

147
00:11:03,330 --> 00:11:08,030
and just start doing things like that, so that I’ll have problems later on.

148
00:11:08,110 --> 00:11:11,650
Because once you do like that, then anybody starts doing.

149
00:11:11,730 --> 00:11:15,470
It’s a kind of an aggressiveness, that you arrange something, come to Me, say.

150
00:11:15,550 --> 00:11:18,155
“Mother, we want to marry.” Now what am I to say?

151
00:11:18,235 --> 00:11:21,900
“All right, marry.” But it creates a problem for Me, for the rest of the people.

152
00:11:21,980 --> 00:11:22,840
They will say, “All right.

153
00:11:22,920 --> 00:11:25,280
If he has married a girl who is twenty years younger,

154
00:11:25,360 --> 00:11:28,660
why not I marry a girl who is thirty years younger?”

155
00:11:28,740 --> 00:11:30,220
You must understand My problems.

156
00:11:30,300 --> 00:11:31,680
If you ask Me for something, “Mother,

157
00:11:31,760 --> 00:11:35,820
should I do it?” You really force Me into it – I have to say “Yes” .

158
00:11:35,900 --> 00:11:39,220
I cannot be very strict with you, because I am your Mother.

159
00:11:39,300 --> 00:11:42,320
But you should be sensible what to ask Me, how far to go.

160
00:11:42,400 --> 00:11:45,370
This is the biggest maryada you have to learn.

161
00:11:45,450 --> 00:11:48,970
Suddenly you will come, “Mother, should I sit here?” What do I say?

162
00:11:49,050 --> 00:11:50,470
Should I make this gentleman sit here?

163
00:11:50,550 --> 00:11:52,616
What should I say? “All right”.

164
00:11:53,120 --> 00:11:56,053
You yourself should not ask such a question.

165
00:11:56,133 --> 00:12:00,040
Because sometimes you give undue importance to somebody, who is “my brother,”

166
00:12:00,120 --> 00:12:03,670
who is “my sister” – something – and make that person sit on My head.

167
00:12:03,750 --> 00:12:09,283
Sometimes you telephone to Me, “Mother, she would like to talk to You.” Who is she?

168
00:12:09,363 --> 00:12:12,020
Is she all right? Should we take her to Mother?

169
00:12:12,100 --> 00:12:14,180
Is she capable of talking to Mother?

170
00:12:14,260 --> 00:12:15,740
What is her condition?

171
00:12:16,100 --> 00:12:17,700
Will she trouble Mother?

172
00:12:17,780 --> 00:12:19,420
Nobody thinks about it!

173
00:12:19,500 --> 00:12:23,800
So you must first establish your relationship with Me of

174
00:12:23,880 --> 00:12:27,640
proper understanding that you should not try to trouble Me.

175
00:12:27,720 --> 00:12:32,580
But this is something is not yet in My hands.

176
00:12:32,660 --> 00:12:36,390
I think because people do not understand what they are doing.

177
00:12:36,470 --> 00:12:40,990
So first try to see that you don’t try to take advantage of Me.

178
00:12:41,070 --> 00:12:46,170
And secondly, don’t try to bring people to Me who do not deserve it.

179
00:12:46,250 --> 00:12:50,490
There is no need to waste My time with them.

180
00:12:50,570 --> 00:12:54,210
I have so much things to be done, so many ideas to be formulated.

181
00:12:54,290 --> 00:12:56,230
I have to work so hard.

182
00:12:56,310 --> 00:13:00,680
You know, I am working harder than any one of you, those who are doing Sahaja Yoga.

183
00:13:00,760 --> 00:13:04,820
And at this age, if you try to trouble Me like that, I don’t know how

184
00:13:04,900 --> 00:13:07,760
to tell you that “Don’t you trouble Me!” In the presence of the person

185
00:13:07,840 --> 00:13:09,780
you will come, you will bring the person on My head, “Oh,

186
00:13:09,860 --> 00:13:14,660
that person has come from Timbuktu, and I have brought her.” Just you do it.

187
00:13:14,740 --> 00:13:16,210
It’s aggressiveness on Me.

188
00:13:16,290 --> 00:13:18,550
Please don’t try to do like this!

189
00:13:18,630 --> 00:13:19,850
This is a wrong thing to do.

190
00:13:19,930 --> 00:13:23,270
So the maryadas are to be established first with Me,

191
00:13:23,350 --> 00:13:27,840
that understand that you should not try to trouble Me at all like this.

192
00:13:27,920 --> 00:13:31,820
Secondly, you must try to please Me by being good people.

193
00:13:33,127 --> 00:13:36,660
I hear that somebody is trying to be very egoistical.

194
00:13:36,740 --> 00:13:41,006
He doesn’t even put on My tapes, he just gives his own lectures.

195
00:13:41,086 --> 00:13:43,280
This kind of a thing is very surprising.

196
00:13:43,360 --> 00:13:44,900
How can people do like that?

197
00:13:46,100 --> 00:13:47,320
Try to bring down your egos, super egos.

198
00:13:47,400 --> 00:13:52,820
You must learn to please Me, “Prasanno bhave Devi, prasanno bhave”.

199
00:13:52,900 --> 00:13:58,100
If you cannot make the Devi Prasanna (pleased), what will be your achievement?

200
00:13:58,334 --> 00:14:00,600
As Rustom says that I am Mahamaya.

201
00:14:00,680 --> 00:14:02,940
All right, but don’t you know that I am that?

202
00:14:03,020 --> 00:14:04,600
So try to keep to it.

203
00:14:04,680 --> 00:14:07,320
And keep that understanding that if you have to grow,

204
00:14:07,400 --> 00:14:10,940
we must have proper relationship with

205
00:14:11,020 --> 00:14:14,740
Mother, and we must understand what will displease Her the most.

206
00:14:14,820 --> 00:14:16,680
“Am I pleasing Her by

207
00:14:16,760 --> 00:14:19,240
doing this?” But if you force Me, “If it pleases You,

208
00:14:19,320 --> 00:14:21,950
we’ll do.” Then what am I to say? “All

209
00:14:22,030 --> 00:14:24,860
right, go ahead.” If it pleases Me I’ll just spontaneously say,

210
00:14:24,940 --> 00:14:27,340
“All right, it pleases Me. Go ahead with it!” Like that,

211
00:14:27,420 --> 00:14:31,680
so many things are there that people just try to force on Me and I say “Yes”.

212
00:14:31,760 --> 00:14:34,540
But I am very cunning and clever in that,

213
00:14:34,620 --> 00:14:39,553
because I tell in a way that you should realise that it is not joy giving.

214
00:14:39,633 --> 00:14:40,940
All right, whatever it is.

215
00:14:41,020 --> 00:14:45,890
Now the second thing is that the maryadas of relationships

216
00:14:45,970 --> 00:14:49,950
between you is a relationship of pure love, of purity.

217
00:14:50,684 --> 00:14:55,750
Unless and until you develop pure relationships, you are going to be ruined!

218
00:14:55,830 --> 00:14:59,090
See, this finger has to have pure relationship with this hand.

219
00:14:59,170 --> 00:15:02,650
Supposing if this finger has some dirty feelings about this hand,

220
00:15:02,730 --> 00:15:05,190
it may dirty it, it may spoil it.

221
00:15:05,270 --> 00:15:11,480
In the same way, we should have extremely pure relationships with each other. Means,

222
00:15:11,560 --> 00:15:17,026
we should try to give our heart to another person without any lust or greed in it.

223
00:15:17,284 --> 00:15:18,950
That we should try to do.

224
00:15:19,030 --> 00:15:20,130
Try to help each other.

225
00:15:20,210 --> 00:15:23,750
I find when they feel in a lusty way,

226
00:15:23,830 --> 00:15:26,310
or a greedy way attached to others – this is not

227
00:15:26,390 --> 00:15:27,110
for the sahaja yogis,

228
00:15:27,190 --> 00:15:30,250
but non sahaja yogis – they get so much interested in that person.

229
00:15:30,330 --> 00:15:32,210
Is a very baser way of attachment.

230
00:15:32,290 --> 00:15:36,070
But in Sahaja Yoga, your attachment is with your Spirit,

231
00:15:36,150 --> 00:15:41,170
with your Atma, and Atma is the purest form of our being.

232
00:15:41,250 --> 00:15:42,970
We have to keep it absolutely pure.

233
00:15:43,050 --> 00:15:48,630
And then the enjoyment is higher than any romance, any marriage, any worldly thing.

234
00:15:48,710 --> 00:15:52,350
It’s the highest and the top-most. First achieve that.

235
00:15:52,430 --> 00:15:56,430
First of all you should arise and achieve that, achieve that purity.

236
00:15:56,510 --> 00:15:58,043
That is very important.

237
00:15:58,123 --> 00:16:03,440
Now the relationship between the men and women, I have told you, that you should

238
00:16:03,520 --> 00:16:09,600
not try to enter into any bedrooms where the ladies are – it’s not proper.

239
00:16:09,820 --> 00:16:14,086
Nor the women should enter into men’s thing. But is very common.

240
00:16:14,166 --> 00:16:17,760
Women should not behave in the way other women behave.

241
00:16:17,840 --> 00:16:21,600
Like, I was told in a wedding in Maharashtra that

242
00:16:21,680 --> 00:16:23,440
the women went and took out all their clothes.

243
00:16:23,520 --> 00:16:24,100
I mean, that’s not England.

244
00:16:24,180 --> 00:16:25,940
They got a shock, you know.

245
00:16:26,020 --> 00:16:28,480
Some of them lost their appetite for three, four days.

246
00:16:28,560 --> 00:16:31,580
They have never seen such women in their lifetime.

247
00:16:31,660 --> 00:16:34,340
They went and took out their clothes suddenly, all of them.

248
00:16:34,420 --> 00:16:36,360
I mean, they were shocked, so much shocked that three,

249
00:16:36,440 --> 00:16:38,780
four days they didn’t eat their food.

250
00:16:38,860 --> 00:16:41,040
So you have no business to shock them also.

251
00:16:41,120 --> 00:16:45,620
Because if you go to somebody’s country, you must know in what way they live.

252
00:16:45,700 --> 00:16:48,060
It’s never done. Nobody becomes nude like that.

253
00:16:48,140 --> 00:16:52,760
And about twenty girls, if suddenly they become nude, what will happen?

254
00:16:52,840 --> 00:16:56,500
So the sense of shame must be developed among men and women.

255
00:16:56,580 --> 00:16:58,300
It looks nice, it looks beautiful.

256
00:16:58,380 --> 00:17:03,340
It gives you an additional charm if you have the sense of shame,

257
00:17:03,560 --> 00:17:04,960
a little bashfulness.

258
00:17:05,040 --> 00:17:09,890
See, your Princess of Wales is regarded as something beautiful. She is bashful.

259
00:17:09,970 --> 00:17:11,830
Her bashfulness is so natural.

260
00:17:11,910 --> 00:17:17,690
That bashfulness is not there, like a – I don’t know what animal does that,

261
00:17:17,780 --> 00:17:20,239
but somebody who has no shame.

262
00:17:20,319 --> 00:17:22,259
I mean, I just don’t know which one is that.

263
00:17:22,339 --> 00:17:24,580
Everybody has a sense of shame, even animals.

264
00:17:24,660 --> 00:17:26,960
So why shouldn’t we have that sense of shame?

265
00:17:27,040 --> 00:17:32,020
How to behave towards women, how to be… Suddenly there is

266
00:17:32,100 --> 00:17:40,520
no need to just… I have seen one lady going from England to

267
00:17:40,600 --> 00:17:45,480
India, and she just went and put a big slap on the back of Mr.

268
00:17:45,560 --> 00:17:49,493
Modi, “Hello Modi, how are you?” And Modi got such a shock.

269
00:17:51,654 --> 00:17:53,920
She didn’t mean, she was innocent,

270
00:17:54,000 --> 00:17:57,800
but that’s not the way in Sahaja Yoga we are going to behave, like some

271
00:17:57,880 --> 00:18:02,200
sort of a debonair or some sort of a fantastic,

272
00:18:02,280 --> 00:18:06,960
what you call, a modern woman, you see, walking in like that.

273
00:18:07,040 --> 00:18:09,900
One must understand one must have a sense of shame.

274
00:18:09,980 --> 00:18:14,740
How do you talk, even with Me they will talk with a hand like that “Mother,

275
00:18:14,820 --> 00:18:18,620
(?) thing is happening.” But there’s no need to do all that, you see.

276
00:18:18,700 --> 00:18:21,660
Talk in a way that is gentle and beautiful.

277
00:18:21,740 --> 00:18:24,540
The other day I met a very nice taxi fellow.

278
00:18:24,620 --> 00:18:27,620
And I tell you, his gestures and things were so beautiful.

279
00:18:27,700 --> 00:18:30,380
Immediately I said, “He is a realised soul.” He would not say anything

280
00:18:30,460 --> 00:18:33,600
without putting his hand like this, and with his eyes down below.

281
00:18:33,680 --> 00:18:36,970
He would not say something like that, nothing of the kind.

282
00:18:37,050 --> 00:18:40,690
So sweet he was, his whole gesture. He is an Englishman.

283
00:18:40,770 --> 00:18:42,330
Brought up and bred here.

284
00:18:42,410 --> 00:18:45,050
Not a single vulgar word he said.

285
00:18:45,130 --> 00:18:47,690
Like one of your players was so stupid,

286
00:18:47,770 --> 00:18:51,280
when Princess Anne went to meet him he said all kinds of things, you see.

287
00:18:51,360 --> 00:18:54,840
Is a kind of an ego, or stupidity, I don’t know, because,

288
00:18:54,920 --> 00:18:59,910
how you talk, how you speak, everything should be saintly.

289
00:18:59,990 --> 00:19:02,940
You are saints now, do you realise? You are all saints.

290
00:19:03,020 --> 00:19:05,760
So how you behave with dignity towards each other,

291
00:19:05,840 --> 00:19:09,880
how you respect their dignity, how you live, is very important,

292
00:19:09,960 --> 00:19:16,000
and that you should try to maintain in a way that looks like a saintly behavior.

293
00:19:16,080 --> 00:19:17,400
You have to be a saint.

294
00:19:17,480 --> 00:19:20,080
And that is not difficult for you, to take to that,

295
00:19:20,160 --> 00:19:22,260
that you behave in a manner that you are saints.

296
00:19:22,340 --> 00:19:27,740
This is very important I must tell you because I have seen that these maryadas.

297
00:19:27,870 --> 00:19:33,710
It would be killing, it would be absolutely killing Sahaja Yoga,

298
00:19:33,790 --> 00:19:35,970
if you do not keep your maryadas.

299
00:19:36,050 --> 00:19:40,070
That is one of the most essential things one has to be.

300
00:19:40,150 --> 00:19:45,050
I have told you again and again how you dress up,

301
00:19:45,130 --> 00:19:50,820
how you bear yourself up, how you talk, how you listen to others more

302
00:19:50,900 --> 00:19:54,500
than you talk yourself, how you become non-aggressive,

303
00:19:54,960 --> 00:19:59,026
is the best way to impress people and to express Sahaja Yoga.

304
00:19:59,106 --> 00:20:01,740
I tell you, as it is, people have started saying,

305
00:20:01,820 --> 00:20:04,540
“They are very beautiful people, you can see they are very beautiful.

306
00:20:04,620 --> 00:20:06,600
You can see they are very different type.

307
00:20:06,680 --> 00:20:07,940
It’s something different.

308
00:20:08,020 --> 00:20:10,480
They are something great.” People have started saying that.

309
00:20:10,560 --> 00:20:17,340
But still we lack in certain things, like we start going on a plane which

310
00:20:17,420 --> 00:20:25,640
is not suitable to our stature, to our dignity, to our position as saints.

311
00:20:25,720 --> 00:20:28,880
We are all prophets, and prophets have to behave like prophets.

312
00:20:28,960 --> 00:20:31,840
They cannot behave like cheap type people.

313
00:20:31,920 --> 00:20:34,800
So, in that we have to understand the maryadas.

314
00:20:34,880 --> 00:20:39,435
Now the maryaada to your leaders also, you should be respectful.

315
00:20:39,515 --> 00:20:44,110
I have seen that nobody calls anybody – even the children will call somebody,

316
00:20:45,470 --> 00:20:50,270
say, elderly person also – never they, say, call them uncle or anything.

317
00:20:50,350 --> 00:20:53,290
It’s a wrong thing. You must teach your children to call elders

318
00:20:53,370 --> 00:20:56,550
by the name as brother or uncle or someone.

319
00:20:56,807 --> 00:20:58,940
Give some respect to the elders.

320
00:20:59,020 --> 00:21:03,040
But when the leader is also not respected, what is the question of it?

321
00:21:03,120 --> 00:21:07,120
I have seen little boys calling big,

322
00:21:07,200 --> 00:21:09,960
married people with three, four children, by name.

323
00:21:10,040 --> 00:21:12,780
That’s not our style. You should never do it.

324
00:21:12,860 --> 00:21:16,140
I saw this – even My husband’s office has this problem.

325
00:21:16,220 --> 00:21:19,380
Because when I came, you see, they always called you by name.

326
00:21:19,460 --> 00:21:22,440
“Tom”- he’s such a big man, he’s called as “Tom”, and all that.

327
00:21:22,520 --> 00:21:25,700
So C.P. looked at it like that you see.

328
00:21:25,780 --> 00:21:30,740
And we always call them – even the drivers, we call them by the name “Mr.,” you see.

329
00:21:30,820 --> 00:21:33,240
So we couldn’t understand why is it like this.

330
00:21:33,320 --> 00:21:37,010
You see, being democratic or something like this,

331
00:21:37,090 --> 00:21:40,240
you see, that’s how you become demonocratic. We must respect.

332
00:21:40,480 --> 00:21:44,640
We must respect each other, must call them by higher names.

333
00:21:44,720 --> 00:21:49,200
Specially when in a meeting, there are people, you should call them – each other,

334
00:21:49,280 --> 00:21:53,700
even your friends – by “Mr. so and so.” It’s all right for Me to call you.

335
00:21:53,780 --> 00:21:58,280
It would look very funny if I call “Mr. Brown” or “Mr.

336
00:21:58,360 --> 00:22:01,020
Reeves” because they are My children, you see, I’m their Mother.

337
00:22:01,100 --> 00:22:04,020
But for you, because you are equal, this thing,

338
00:22:04,100 --> 00:22:08,180
at least call them “Mr.” and say something in a way which is good.

339
00:22:08,260 --> 00:22:11,460
Like the English language has many words as “please”,

340
00:22:11,540 --> 00:22:15,860
“thank you.” All these must be used profusely, profusely.

341
00:22:15,940 --> 00:22:17,800
We are going back a little bit.

342
00:22:17,880 --> 00:22:19,880
We are now becoming much more modern.

343
00:22:19,960 --> 00:22:24,460
That we should give up and become less modern and more elevating.

344
00:22:24,840 --> 00:22:34,240
Now the whole idea of this maryada is such that

345
00:22:34,320 --> 00:22:37,180
when you have called somebody as a sister or a

346
00:22:37,260 --> 00:22:41,230
brother then it is not only lip service – “You are

347
00:22:41,310 --> 00:22:45,640
my sister” – it is something innate, and very deep.

348
00:22:45,720 --> 00:22:51,430
You have to develop that feeling of a sister, because that’s how your sublimity

349
00:22:51,510 --> 00:22:55,440
will go up, your left Vishuddhi will improve, your Vishnumaya will be satisfied.

350
00:22:55,520 --> 00:22:57,440
If you call somebody a sister,

351
00:22:57,520 --> 00:23:01,020
the sisterly and the daughterly relationships, and motherly

352
00:23:01,100 --> 00:23:03,360
relationships, always bring down, you see,

353
00:23:03,440 --> 00:23:09,140
the so-called ego, which is hiding in the left Vishuddhi.

354
00:23:09,220 --> 00:23:14,060
So try to be kind and gentle with the person whom you call the sister.

355
00:23:14,140 --> 00:23:15,800
Stand by her, look after her.

356
00:23:15,880 --> 00:23:21,030
If somebody you call your brother, you have to pray for his protection,

357
00:23:21,110 --> 00:23:27,070
then you must know that you have a right to ask him for his protection also.

358
00:23:27,150 --> 00:23:31,910
But you must also give something to him, and you must try to look after him,

359
00:23:31,990 --> 00:23:36,010
welcome him to your house, and treat him as a

360
00:23:36,090 --> 00:23:40,430
somebody, a part and parcel of your being, because he’s very much

361
00:23:40,510 --> 00:23:43,590
near to you because he is your brother, and he’s very much closer.

362
00:23:43,670 --> 00:23:46,750
But such a brother should not try to dominate the wife.

363
00:23:46,830 --> 00:23:48,970
This is the maryada, again.

364
00:23:49,050 --> 00:23:53,830
Like a brother is, somehow, is very friendly with the brother, or a lady is friendly

365
00:23:53,910 --> 00:23:58,630
as a sister, then she should not try to put a wedge between the husband and wife.

366
00:23:58,710 --> 00:24:02,250
That is the worst thing to do, is to put a wedge between husband and wife.

367
00:24:02,330 --> 00:24:05,830
Anybody who tries that must know that he’s a mean person.

368
00:24:05,910 --> 00:24:09,130
One should never try to put a wedge between husband and wife.

369
00:24:09,210 --> 00:24:12,390
I know there are problems between husband and wife, I’ll put them right.

370
00:24:12,470 --> 00:24:14,730
But you don’t try to put any wedge between them.

371
00:24:14,810 --> 00:24:16,550
And don’t try to create a problem.

372
00:24:16,630 --> 00:24:21,110
If it is problematic, it is for Me to solve, not you people don’t have to solve.

373
00:24:21,190 --> 00:24:23,750
And don’t interfere with their married life.

374
00:24:23,830 --> 00:24:25,310
Let them be as they are.

375
00:24:25,390 --> 00:24:28,670
I will find out how they are, I’ll try to help them.

376
00:24:28,750 --> 00:24:33,450
But it’s very wrong to play with their married life or with their married problems,

377
00:24:33,530 --> 00:24:35,330
and suddenly jump on somebody.

378
00:24:35,410 --> 00:24:37,670
Is a very wrong thing, which is very common here.

379
00:24:37,750 --> 00:24:41,450
And [if] a woman is in distress, you see, a man will come to help her,

380
00:24:41,530 --> 00:24:44,360
even if she is married, he’ll elope with her.

381
00:24:44,440 --> 00:24:47,010
This is how he comes to help her in the distress,

382
00:24:47,090 --> 00:24:49,550
to create another distress for her!

383
00:24:50,060 --> 00:24:54,420
So this is how one should understand that this kind of a cheap

384
00:24:54,500 --> 00:24:59,040
heart giving business, and taking business, is not for Sahaja Yoga.

385
00:25:00,610 --> 00:25:02,990
In our heart resides the Spirit.

386
00:25:03,860 --> 00:25:05,460
We are dignified people,

387
00:25:05,540 --> 00:25:12,050
and in that dignity we have to rise and live with that dignity.

388
00:25:12,130 --> 00:25:17,520
Not to cheaply allow the Spirit to be insulted or dominated or subjugated to anyone.

389
00:25:17,600 --> 00:25:21,450
Now the relationship with children also one should understand.

390
00:25:21,530 --> 00:25:26,710
I have seen some people have a habit of getting a child very much closer,

391
00:25:26,790 --> 00:25:30,830
and pampering them, “Oh, that child is this thing.

392
00:25:30,910 --> 00:25:33,790
Oh, that child…” Let the parents handle the child,

393
00:25:33,870 --> 00:25:36,850
you just don’t interfere with other’s children.

394
00:25:36,930 --> 00:25:38,690
Don’t interfere much with them.

395
00:25:38,770 --> 00:25:42,930
If you find any child is such and such, inform Me, I’ll cure the child.

396
00:25:43,010 --> 00:25:45,510
But if a child is being spoilt by you,

397
00:25:45,590 --> 00:25:49,310
it’s the worst thing to do is to harm that child, is to spoil.

398
00:25:49,390 --> 00:25:54,290
Children here are very clever and intelligent, you must know.

399
00:25:54,390 --> 00:25:56,723
They are very good at manipulating.

400
00:25:56,803 --> 00:25:59,770
They will, because they are extremely precocious.

401
00:25:59,850 --> 00:26:03,970
They are realised souls, they are born in this country. What a combination!

402
00:26:04,050 --> 00:26:07,470
At that time you must be very careful as to their training.

403
00:26:07,550 --> 00:26:13,250
From the first five years all the parents must be extremely strict with children,

404
00:26:13,330 --> 00:26:19,670
extremely strict. Don’t allow them to overpower you or manoeuvre, manipulate you.

405
00:26:20,770 --> 00:26:22,170
It’s very important.

406
00:26:22,250 --> 00:26:27,350
If you allow them to overpower you or to dominate you, they’ll sit on your head.

407
00:26:27,430 --> 00:26:28,870
Tell them not to do like that.

408
00:26:28,950 --> 00:26:32,890
And one day you will come and say, “Mother, what to do, these are realised

409
00:26:32,970 --> 00:26:37,430
souls and, you see, we were looking after them.” They are not deities!

410
00:26:37,510 --> 00:26:39,930
They are not deities to be worshipped!

411
00:26:40,010 --> 00:26:41,550
They are only realised souls.

412
00:26:41,630 --> 00:26:42,750
So keep them at that point.

413
00:26:42,830 --> 00:26:46,270
And you are My trustees of those children.

414
00:26:46,350 --> 00:26:49,630
And if you spoil them, it is you who will he held responsible.

415
00:26:49,710 --> 00:26:53,570
You have no business to spoil the lives of these children as sahaja yogis,

416
00:26:53,650 --> 00:26:55,450
and their chances of ascent.

417
00:26:55,530 --> 00:26:58,730
So if they are born-realised, they are not deities – this you must understand.

418
00:26:58,810 --> 00:27:03,720
They are not beyond corruption, they are not beyond all kinds of things.

419
00:27:04,490 --> 00:27:07,490
So this, if you understand this little point,

420
00:27:07,570 --> 00:27:10,770
that dealing with your children you have to be really strict.

421
00:27:10,850 --> 00:27:14,110
They must know how to meditate, they must know how to pray,

422
00:27:14,190 --> 00:27:18,470
they must know how to respect; and all the good things you must teach your children.

423
00:27:18,550 --> 00:27:20,770
And don’t allow them to sit on your head.

424
00:27:20,850 --> 00:27:24,030
Many people have ruined the lives of their children like this.

425
00:27:24,110 --> 00:27:28,730
Now will you please see that such child is brought into proper level?

426
00:27:28,810 --> 00:27:31,490
If the child is trying to take liberties with you,

427
00:27:31,570 --> 00:27:35,490
and cheeky and does not listen, please give that child to

428
00:27:35,570 --> 00:27:37,310
some other sahaja yogi to look after,

429
00:27:37,390 --> 00:27:41,330
whom you think can look after, and see that the child is put right.

430
00:27:41,410 --> 00:27:43,030
Nip in the bud is the best way,

431
00:27:43,110 --> 00:27:46,680
because we don’t want to have children who are spoilt,

432
00:27:46,760 --> 00:27:49,720
who are spoiling other children,

433
00:27:49,800 --> 00:27:53,940
nor we want children who are subjected to such children.

434
00:27:54,020 --> 00:27:59,960
So, you can have proper children, well-behaved children, sensible, wise children.

435
00:28:00,040 --> 00:28:04,120
Because they can really be a drag on you, on Me,

436
00:28:04,200 --> 00:28:07,200
on everyone, if you do not properly bring them up.

437
00:28:07,280 --> 00:28:11,070
And they are our liabilities; we have to look after them.

438
00:28:11,150 --> 00:28:14,870
So the relationship between the father and children,

439
00:28:14,950 --> 00:28:17,390
mother and children, is important.

440
00:28:17,470 --> 00:28:20,210
Actually the mother should look after the child much more.

441
00:28:20,290 --> 00:28:21,810
And the child must respect.

442
00:28:21,890 --> 00:28:24,450
Father should never scold the mother in the presence of the child.

443
00:28:24,530 --> 00:28:28,550
That’s one thing one must understand, that, if the father starts scolding the

444
00:28:28,630 --> 00:28:31,830
mother in the presence of the child, the child will have no respect for the mother.

445
00:28:31,910 --> 00:28:36,210
But the respect must be maintained, because if the wife respects the husband,

446
00:28:36,290 --> 00:28:39,516
then the child will know how to respect her and the husband too.

447
00:28:40,250 --> 00:28:43,070
So the whole thing is built up like that.

448
00:28:43,150 --> 00:28:46,170
Is a kind of a pattern for children to follow.

449
00:28:46,250 --> 00:28:51,730
One should not try to dominate the husband, at least in the presence of children.

450
00:28:52,410 --> 00:28:53,690
It is very wrong,

451
00:28:53,770 --> 00:28:57,950
because then the children learn that trick and they start dominating you.

452
00:28:58,030 --> 00:28:59,750
So it flows from you to children.

453
00:28:59,830 --> 00:29:04,330
So try to see that if you have to do anything then you do it yourself.

454
00:29:04,410 --> 00:29:08,230
And respect the husband and in a way that is very obvious

455
00:29:08,310 --> 00:29:11,770
to the child that the father is respected by mother.

456
00:29:11,850 --> 00:29:13,916
And they are just like monkeys.

457
00:29:14,467 --> 00:29:16,600
The way you behave, they behave.

458
00:29:16,680 --> 00:29:20,560
So you allow them to behave in a particular manner, they will behave that way.

459
00:29:20,640 --> 00:29:22,540
But if you put a good pattern…

460
00:29:22,620 --> 00:29:27,880
The other day I was thinking, how Indian children are so obedient, so sensible.

461
00:29:27,960 --> 00:29:34,265
They will never ask for it. “I want this, I want that.” They never manipulate.

462
00:29:34,345 --> 00:29:37,450
What happens? What happens, how do they do it?

463
00:29:37,530 --> 00:29:40,410
The reason is, I think, is a good pattern in the house.

464
00:29:40,490 --> 00:29:44,690
Everybody knows whom to respect, how to respect, how to behave.

465
00:29:44,770 --> 00:29:51,745
The relationship in Sahaja Yoga has to be even more than this, much more subtler.

466
00:29:51,825 --> 00:29:56,000
For example, if – this I’ve said before also – if we are in a room,

467
00:29:56,080 --> 00:30:00,640
try to give another person a room always, try to. Try to do for them.

468
00:30:00,720 --> 00:30:06,120
If you have to pay, better pay yourself, not that wait for another person to pay.

469
00:30:06,200 --> 00:30:09,320
Try to do it yourself, run forward to do it.

470
00:30:09,400 --> 00:30:13,360
You see, if someone is carrying the luggage, you run, you do it.

471
00:30:13,440 --> 00:30:15,140
That is the way a sahaja yogi should be.

472
00:30:15,220 --> 00:30:16,440
Mostly, children are like that.

473
00:30:16,520 --> 00:30:17,720
They’ll say, “I’ll get it, I’ll do it,

474
00:30:17,800 --> 00:30:21,360
I’ll receive it.” May be ego, you might call it, but whatever it is,

475
00:30:21,440 --> 00:30:27,400
but that is the style you all have to achieve by organising

476
00:30:27,480 --> 00:30:32,460
a proper type of an image for the whole society.

477
00:30:32,540 --> 00:30:35,500
That if somebody needs something, you run away. “You want water?

478
00:30:35,580 --> 00:30:36,400
All right… You want this thing?

479
00:30:36,480 --> 00:30:38,900
You take mine.” Food also – same thing.

480
00:30:38,980 --> 00:30:42,480
First let others have, not that you should first have anything.

481
00:30:42,560 --> 00:30:44,700
How you eat your food is very important,

482
00:30:44,780 --> 00:30:50,570
everything is very important for the children to see, and to behave like that.

483
00:30:50,920 --> 00:30:55,380
In money matters also, I have seen that people should be very,

484
00:30:55,460 --> 00:30:58,640
very sensible and should have proper maryadas.

485
00:30:59,320 --> 00:31:04,350
Now with Me, whatever maryadas you want to keep, you must understand,

486
00:31:04,430 --> 00:31:06,150
because [it’s] very embarrassing to talk about it.

487
00:31:06,230 --> 00:31:08,310
But so far, as you know that,

488
00:31:08,390 --> 00:31:12,930
I had to shell out lot of money to manage many funds, many things.

489
00:31:13,010 --> 00:31:17,530
And last time also we had many people who came (?) doesn’t matter.

490
00:31:17,610 --> 00:31:23,070
But now as it is…would you not do just now!

491
00:31:23,150 --> 00:31:25,610
In My lecture why should you do?

492
00:31:26,260 --> 00:31:31,490
At the time, now, when we are talking about maryadas, we must know that,

493
00:31:31,570 --> 00:31:36,150
in any case, Mother should not be made to pay anymore.

494
00:31:36,230 --> 00:31:39,770
Because we are so many, we should try to manage, if possible.

495
00:31:39,850 --> 00:31:43,330
Like yesterday, I had a person from BBC, and he said,

496
00:31:43,410 --> 00:31:47,390
“It is wrong of You not to take any money from them.” I said, “Where is the money?

497
00:31:47,470 --> 00:31:52,130
No question of taking, I have to pay Myself.” I said,

498
00:31:52,210 --> 00:31:55,090
“It is so invaluable that how can you charge for it?

499
00:31:55,170 --> 00:31:57,330
You cannot charge for it, it is very invaluable.

500
00:31:57,410 --> 00:32:02,510
The Spirit is very invaluable, and you cannot charge for it.” So he was insisting.

501
00:32:02,590 --> 00:32:04,670
I mean, he took half an hour on this subject only.

502
00:32:04,750 --> 00:32:09,650
He said, “This Anglo-Saxon brain won’t understand unless and until You

503
00:32:09,730 --> 00:32:16,150
make it a little more money-oriented or something.” I said, “I cannot.

504
00:32:16,230 --> 00:32:19,930
Tell me how much is to be paid.” Just to shut him down, I said, “What about Christ?

505
00:32:20,010 --> 00:32:21,780
How much money did He take?

506
00:32:21,860 --> 00:32:26,300
By God’s grace I am quite well off and I really don’t need either.

507
00:32:26,380 --> 00:32:31,080
But He needed, still He never took any money from anyone.” Then he kept quiet.

508
00:32:31,160 --> 00:32:37,000
But this is what it is, you see, that people think that you are getting it easy,

509
00:32:37,080 --> 00:32:42,800
cheap and that’s why you want to take advantage, which is wrong.

510
00:32:44,310 --> 00:32:45,600
You must respect.

511
00:32:46,420 --> 00:32:54,210
You must respect and understand that it is never good to take any advantage of Me.

512
00:32:54,340 --> 00:32:58,360
On the contrary, whenever it is possible we should try to do

513
00:32:58,440 --> 00:33:03,580
whatever is possible for Sahaja Yoga – is very important. Try to surrender.

514
00:33:03,660 --> 00:33:06,560
Not that I will take any money from you, you know that.

515
00:33:06,640 --> 00:33:07,960
I don’t want any money or anything.

516
00:33:08,040 --> 00:33:11,340
But surrender yourself absolutely to Sahaja Yoga.

517
00:33:11,420 --> 00:33:15,420
That’s the best way people have risen and have done so well.

518
00:33:15,900 --> 00:33:19,760
Now the relationship among yourselves,

519
00:33:21,210 --> 00:33:26,600
among different groups, among different nations.

520
00:33:27,140 --> 00:33:33,380
We should try to help people who, supposing there is a couple now,

521
00:33:33,460 --> 00:33:35,860
wants to go to India to get married.

522
00:33:35,940 --> 00:33:38,040
Now if they don’t have money, of course I am there.

523
00:33:38,120 --> 00:33:39,860
I said, “All right, they need not pay any money,

524
00:33:39,940 --> 00:33:45,160
I’ll pay for them.” But Warren has put down his foot, he says, “Why

525
00:33:45,240 --> 00:33:50,510
not the people, or the centre, help them out,

526
00:33:50,590 --> 00:33:53,890
for the time being?” You see because they helped; now supposing they

527
00:33:53,970 --> 00:33:56,610
have helped somebody – he had no money, he went to India,

528
00:33:56,690 --> 00:34:00,290
he got married and then he got lost, you see, he misbehaved,

529
00:34:00,370 --> 00:34:03,710
in the sense, he doesn’t talk to anyone, he thinks no end of himself,

530
00:34:03,790 --> 00:34:06,110
then he started behaving in a funny manner.

531
00:34:06,190 --> 00:34:10,690
So a kind of a feeling came into their mind that “Why should we do it?

532
00:34:10,770 --> 00:34:13,440
If you do it for somebody, he behaves like this.

533
00:34:13,520 --> 00:34:17,520
If you try to help somebody…” Is this a natural reaction that if

534
00:34:17,600 --> 00:34:22,540
you try to do something for someone then people try to misbehave? That’s not so.

535
00:34:22,620 --> 00:34:26,680
Must be one person has done it, that doesn’t mean that everybody has done it.

536
00:34:26,760 --> 00:34:27,860
That’s what it is.

537
00:34:27,940 --> 00:34:33,860
They say that a kind of a barrier is built in a person who is helped by us, and his

538
00:34:33,940 --> 00:34:37,980
ego is challenged, and he tries to behave in a manner which was never known before.

539
00:34:38,060 --> 00:34:41,960
And he starts behaving in such a funny manner that he doesn’t talk to anyone,

540
00:34:42,040 --> 00:34:47,040
he keeps out and he becomes mad with his ego. So his ego is hurt.

541
00:34:47,120 --> 00:34:48,300
There’s nothing to feel hurt.

542
00:34:48,380 --> 00:34:52,520
Because if you have no money and if it is one part and one body,

543
00:34:52,600 --> 00:34:54,400
if somebody’s helping you out, doesn’t matter.

544
00:34:54,480 --> 00:34:56,800
You can help, when you are well off, to somebody else.

545
00:34:56,880 --> 00:34:58,760
But when it comes to you, you give up.

546
00:34:58,840 --> 00:35:03,200
So this is a very absurd type of a behavior of one individual,

547
00:35:03,280 --> 00:35:05,660
or two or three, or maybe five or ten. Doesn’t matter.

548
00:35:05,740 --> 00:35:07,820
But still we must not forget that we have to help.

549
00:35:07,900 --> 00:35:11,100
We have to help as many as possible.

550
00:35:11,180 --> 00:35:15,680
And we must try to do whatever is possible for us, for others. This is important.

551
00:35:15,760 --> 00:35:19,260
If we cannot do for a group, like sahaja yogis, whom are we going to help?

552
00:35:19,340 --> 00:35:21,010
So we have to give that help.

553
00:35:21,090 --> 00:35:22,970
Now in Sahaja Yoga itself,

554
00:35:23,050 --> 00:35:27,210
on the subtle basis we should not try to judge anybody’s vibrations.

555
00:35:27,290 --> 00:35:30,470
It is very common in people, “Oh, you are caught up on your Agnya.

556
00:35:30,550 --> 00:35:32,630
Oh, you have got this wrong, let me clear you out.

557
00:35:32,710 --> 00:35:35,630
You sit down.” Morning till evening, without meditating,

558
00:35:35,710 --> 00:35:38,590
they are clearing each other’s chakras and catching on themselves.

559
00:35:38,670 --> 00:35:40,670
It’s an absolutely wrong idea.

560
00:35:40,750 --> 00:35:43,610
Everybody, individually, should sit before the photograph,

561
00:35:43,690 --> 00:35:46,770
get the vibrations, every morning, there should be a discipline.

562
00:35:46,850 --> 00:35:50,750
You must know that the system of Sahaja Yoga today has worked out this way that

563
00:35:50,830 --> 00:35:55,310
I have given you Realisation just to say that – let your light be enlightened.

564
00:35:55,390 --> 00:35:57,930
Now you have to see your lamp, if it is clean or not.

565
00:35:58,010 --> 00:36:00,150
Only possible when the light is enlightened.

566
00:36:00,230 --> 00:36:03,055
See your lamp, if it is enlightened or not.

567
00:36:03,135 --> 00:36:06,100
See, if somebody is over-aggressive, then it’s all right,

568
00:36:06,180 --> 00:36:09,060
you make a joint attack on that person, and tell-off that person.

569
00:36:09,140 --> 00:36:10,760
Or there are leaders who will do it.

570
00:36:10,840 --> 00:36:13,140
But everybody should not judge others.

571
00:36:13,220 --> 00:36:16,740
You better judge yourself, cleanse yourself, look after yourself,

572
00:36:16,820 --> 00:36:20,360
and also try to see how your lamp is – is it clean?

573
00:36:20,440 --> 00:36:23,420
Mother has given us the light to see and why not see?

574
00:36:23,500 --> 00:36:27,520
So if you work it out on these lines, you’ll go very fast.

575
00:36:27,920 --> 00:36:30,560
And you have to, now, perfect yourself.

576
00:36:30,640 --> 00:36:32,250
We have so many sahaja yogis.

577
00:36:32,330 --> 00:36:34,150
But how many are perfect?

578
00:36:34,230 --> 00:36:35,230
This is the point is.

579
00:36:35,310 --> 00:36:38,210
Now your relationship to Sahaja Yoga is also very important.

580
00:36:38,290 --> 00:36:40,530
There’s a maryada about it very much.

581
00:36:40,610 --> 00:36:42,750
Sahaja Yoga should not be taken for granted.

582
00:36:42,830 --> 00:36:45,390
Anybody who thinks he has got Realisation and now

583
00:36:45,470 --> 00:36:47,750
he is sitting on top of the world – is not so.

584
00:36:47,830 --> 00:36:51,390
You must work it out, you have to have discipline.

585
00:36:51,470 --> 00:36:55,270
The same gentleman, the BBC fellow, was saying that it was before,

586
00:36:55,350 --> 00:37:00,090
for years together, you had to live in celibacy and wash the feet of

587
00:37:00,170 --> 00:37:06,900
the …wash the steps of the temple and do all kinds of things, work hard,

588
00:37:06,980 --> 00:37:11,640
do this, do that – and then they would raise it to one chakra. I said,

589
00:37:11,720 --> 00:37:17,680
“Now we do it the other way round!” First build the dome and then the foundation.

590
00:37:18,714 --> 00:37:20,380
Sahaja Yoga is like that.

591
00:37:20,460 --> 00:37:23,520
So that with the dome you understand, you are protected, you are looked after.

592
00:37:23,600 --> 00:37:28,510
But people take it for granted, like. “Mother will do it.

593
00:37:28,590 --> 00:37:31,260
Leave it to Mother.” No, it is not so. You are My hands.

594
00:37:31,340 --> 00:37:34,460
Supposing My hands have to lift this, I should say that Nirmala will do it?

595
00:37:34,540 --> 00:37:38,400
Now, which is Nirmala? These hands are the Nirmala at this point.

596
00:37:38,480 --> 00:37:41,280
So, many people drift like that.

597
00:37:41,360 --> 00:37:46,200
So, to Sahaja Yoga also, your attitude should be of respect.

598
00:37:46,337 --> 00:37:51,470
You should not try to put yourself into bandhan before others, you should not

599
00:37:51,550 --> 00:37:55,230
try to do these things, but in a dignified way you must respect Sahaja Yoga.

600
00:37:55,310 --> 00:37:57,670
And foremost of all, to Sahaja Yoga your relationship

601
00:37:57,750 --> 00:38:01,170
should be that you should know Sahaja Yoga, what it is.

602
00:38:01,250 --> 00:38:06,580
Otherwise every time if you have to talk about Sahaja, Gavin must come, or somebody.

603
00:38:06,660 --> 00:38:10,720
Why? Gavin didn’t know a word about Sahaja Yoga, he didn’t know a word about Indian

604
00:38:10,800 --> 00:38:12,580
mythology, he didn’t know anything,

605
00:38:12,660 --> 00:38:16,740
he did not know what Realisation is – he studied. He’s even studying Sanskrit.

606
00:38:16,820 --> 00:38:18,460
Like many of you have done it.

607
00:38:18,540 --> 00:38:22,680
But all of you, one and all, should become a big pandit.

608
00:38:22,760 --> 00:38:25,480
But you get lost in your marriage problems.

609
00:38:25,560 --> 00:38:27,440
Then your children’s problems.

610
00:38:27,520 --> 00:38:31,660
Then “my mother,” then “my sister.” I mean, it will take too much time for you.

611
00:38:31,740 --> 00:38:33,840
First of all you should see, “I am a sahaja yogi.

612
00:38:33,920 --> 00:38:37,000
Let me get to work.” And it creates problems for us also.

613
00:38:37,080 --> 00:38:40,700
Because your wife will sue you, your children will come round, this, that.

614
00:38:40,780 --> 00:38:44,050
You should say, “I have nothing to do, I am going to study Sahaja Yoga.” I was

615
00:38:44,130 --> 00:38:49,740
surprised that many people have taken The Advent just like as a Bible,

616
00:38:50,674 --> 00:38:51,940
They never read it.

617
00:38:52,020 --> 00:38:56,930
I was surprised that some people do not know what I have written in the Bible.

618
00:38:57,010 --> 00:39:01,230
So it is like the Jews, you see, having a Golden Bible tied up here.

619
00:39:01,310 --> 00:39:07,790
They keep The Advent in a very good cover near the photograph,

620
00:39:07,870 --> 00:39:08,950
worship it – finished.

621
00:39:09,030 --> 00:39:14,110
Then the knowledge goes into them straight away!

622
00:39:14,190 --> 00:39:18,910
You must read some chapters at least of Advent, if not anything else.

623
00:39:18,990 --> 00:39:21,210
There are so many books you can read [that] I have told you.

624
00:39:21,290 --> 00:39:23,270
Try to make your own library.

625
00:39:23,350 --> 00:39:24,590
Try to improve in it.

626
00:39:24,670 --> 00:39:27,770
Everybody must try to get perfection it – perfectionism.

627
00:39:27,850 --> 00:39:31,910
You should never be a liability on Sahaja Yoga, but a great asset of Sahaja Yoga.

628
00:39:31,990 --> 00:39:33,850
That’s what everybody should try to be.

629
00:39:33,930 --> 00:39:36,090
That, your problems I will solve.

630
00:39:36,170 --> 00:39:37,930
But you solve your ascent.

631
00:39:38,010 --> 00:39:43,570
they go into an ashram, and then they think this is their house.

632
00:39:43,650 --> 00:39:48,380
They live there, they manipulate all the money that they save and this and that,

633
00:39:48,460 --> 00:39:51,840
and develop this, want to make everything comfortable.

634
00:39:51,920 --> 00:39:54,860
They never think that, “This is not my ashram.

635
00:39:54,940 --> 00:39:57,370
I am doing it because I am a sahaja yogi.

636
00:39:57,450 --> 00:39:59,060
This is the Ashram of Mother.

637
00:39:59,140 --> 00:40:02,560
I have to do it.” But that detachment is not there.

638
00:40:03,290 --> 00:40:05,670
Not at all a detachment.

639
00:40:05,750 --> 00:40:10,710
And it is something surprising, that if you have to go to Himalayas and

640
00:40:10,790 --> 00:40:15,523
make an insurance policy, then what’s the use of coming to Sahaja Yoga?

641
00:40:17,320 --> 00:40:22,120
It is as absurd as that, that we are writing to insurance policies,

642
00:40:22,200 --> 00:40:23,520
that “I have gone to Himalayas.

643
00:40:23,600 --> 00:40:26,420
When I die, give my property to this one.

644
00:40:26,500 --> 00:40:31,020
If I don’t die, I’ll come back after that.” And nicely

645
00:40:31,100 --> 00:40:35,640
packing up in a nice plastic bag so that ice doesn’t spoil it.

646
00:40:37,900 --> 00:40:39,660
It’s as absurd as that!

647
00:40:40,180 --> 00:40:42,440
So you should not have anything.

648
00:40:42,520 --> 00:40:45,820
Now some people have a habit, “Oh, I’ll get a house for myself.

649
00:40:45,900 --> 00:40:50,320
Get my wife there, children there, finished!.” All such people should, for a change,

650
00:40:50,400 --> 00:40:54,920
leave their houses, come to ashram, put some other people in their house.

651
00:40:55,000 --> 00:40:56,560
Because they are getting attached, you see.

652
00:40:56,640 --> 00:40:58,373
How will you get detached?

653
00:40:59,700 --> 00:41:01,100
Is there any way out?

654
00:41:01,180 --> 00:41:03,320
That is very important in Sahaja Yoga.

655
00:41:03,400 --> 00:41:05,420
Unless and until you are detached, you cannot ascend.

656
00:41:05,500 --> 00:41:08,740
Supposing you have all the tentacles down here on the Mother Earth,

657
00:41:08,820 --> 00:41:12,153
and you say, “Let this plane fly,” how will it go?

658
00:41:12,540 --> 00:41:15,540
So those people who have houses of their own,

659
00:41:15,620 --> 00:41:19,080
or buildings of their own or anything – flats – should give up their houses.

660
00:41:19,160 --> 00:41:21,200
Not to be that comfortable. Get out of it.

661
00:41:21,280 --> 00:41:24,840
Ask some other people to shift, and you shift to the ashram.

662
00:41:24,920 --> 00:41:28,050
Go on shifting, training your mind to shift,

663
00:41:28,130 --> 00:41:31,985
to live with everyone, to be able to share and to do things.

664
00:41:32,065 --> 00:41:36,820
I have changed forty houses after My marriage, you can imagine.

665
00:41:38,240 --> 00:41:40,900
What a very multi-purpose house.

666
00:41:40,980 --> 00:41:45,840
And I have changed, so far, forty houses, and if I change now this house,

667
00:41:45,920 --> 00:41:48,380
Hester’s (Hester Spiro) house, it will be the forty-first.

668
00:41:48,460 --> 00:41:54,000
You can imagine, I have been married forty years and forty houses I have changed.

669
00:41:54,080 --> 00:41:57,486
So the relationship of purity must be understood, in everything.

670
00:41:57,580 --> 00:41:59,180
Is it pure relationship?

671
00:41:59,350 --> 00:42:04,350
Am I living in this ashram in pure relationship? “Because this is the house

672
00:42:04,430 --> 00:42:07,390
that is giving me comfort, that’s why I am living in this house, or am I

673
00:42:07,470 --> 00:42:12,655
just living here, just because it’s an abode – I am here today, and I will

674
00:42:12,735 --> 00:42:16,560
be there tomorrow?” You will be amazed, you will enjoy every part of life.

675
00:42:16,760 --> 00:42:19,693
As soon as you are attached, you are doomed!

676
00:42:19,857 --> 00:42:22,790
It’s a headache to be attached to something.

677
00:42:22,870 --> 00:42:25,270
Then you hanker. “My wife has not arrived.

678
00:42:25,350 --> 00:42:27,010
Oh God, what to do now?

679
00:42:27,090 --> 00:42:28,550
I must telephone to her,

680
00:42:28,630 --> 00:42:32,900
get her here.” But if you are detached about it – she’ll come in time.

681
00:42:32,980 --> 00:42:35,220
Not only that, but you will enjoy her company.

682
00:42:35,300 --> 00:42:37,680
Otherwise you’ll shout at her, “Why didn’t you come in time?

683
00:42:37,760 --> 00:42:42,060
I was waiting for you.” Then why were you waiting to scold her,

684
00:42:42,140 --> 00:42:44,710
and shout at her and spoil all the relationship?

685
00:42:44,790 --> 00:42:48,856
Just see, the absurdity of the whole thing is the attachment.

686
00:42:48,950 --> 00:42:54,550
You should get completely detached about everything, and you will enjoy, just enjoy.

687
00:42:54,630 --> 00:42:56,070
But in that also,

688
00:42:56,150 --> 00:43:00,930
one has to judge – you are really enjoying or you are just making a drama out of it?

689
00:43:01,010 --> 00:43:05,710
Try to be sincere. Purity is brought forth by sincerity.

690
00:43:05,790 --> 00:43:10,450
If you are not sincere to yourself and to others, you cannot be pure.

691
00:43:10,530 --> 00:43:14,796
And purity is the main thing you have to achieve in Sahaja Yoga,

692
00:43:14,876 --> 00:43:17,410
apart from the unity, which I have given you.

693
00:43:17,490 --> 00:43:21,023
But if you do not use this unity for purity – no use.

694
00:43:22,310 --> 00:43:29,450
So this light should give you complete wisdom that you enjoy a pure, good life.

695
00:43:29,910 --> 00:43:34,690
You are married, all right, you have life of enjoyment with your wife;

696
00:43:34,770 --> 00:43:38,220
that I have already described to you.

697
00:43:38,637 --> 00:43:41,170
And with your wife how to behave also,

698
00:43:41,250 --> 00:43:45,183
I have described to you many a times, or with your husband.

699
00:43:45,480 --> 00:43:47,600
But when it comes to others,

700
00:43:48,080 --> 00:43:53,920
you should have absolutely pure relationship of no exploitation.

701
00:43:54,000 --> 00:44:00,600
Even there are flirting exploitations, as the same as money exploitations.

702
00:44:00,680 --> 00:44:03,600
Here if you exploit somebody by money it’s called a thug,

703
00:44:03,680 --> 00:44:05,240
but flirting is not called anything.

704
00:44:05,580 --> 00:44:08,560
I think that is a much worse crime, according to Christ.

705
00:44:08,640 --> 00:44:11,520
So you have to be careful on this point,

706
00:44:11,600 --> 00:44:16,460
and understand that relationship with each other has to be clear.

707
00:44:17,450 --> 00:44:22,250
Now there are people who have, say, horrible wives or horrible husbands.

708
00:44:22,330 --> 00:44:24,660
I don’t mind, they can give them up.

709
00:44:24,740 --> 00:44:28,220
If they are absolutely impossible, if they are spoiling their purity,

710
00:44:28,300 --> 00:44:34,060
if they are torturing their lives, then is best is to get rid of them, I don’t mind.

711
00:44:34,140 --> 00:44:38,400
Because if they are so bad that you cannot use them – just like this body, if it

712
00:44:38,480 --> 00:44:43,640
is so bad, it’s better to give up and die – so that let that relationship die out.

713
00:44:43,720 --> 00:44:48,160
But that death should come to you as a very forceful help, otherwise,

714
00:44:48,240 --> 00:44:52,250
after that, if you become a nervous personality, what’s the use?

715
00:44:52,330 --> 00:44:55,380
So what you have to do after such a thing has

716
00:44:55,460 --> 00:44:57,920
happened – that you have given up such a relationship

717
00:44:58,000 --> 00:45:00,160
– then, if you have to go to courts and all that,

718
00:45:00,240 --> 00:45:02,460
you should give up Sahaja Yoga for the time being.

719
00:45:02,540 --> 00:45:03,660
Solve your problems.

720
00:45:03,740 --> 00:45:06,420
Solve your court problems, everything, then come to Sahaja Yoga.

721
00:45:06,500 --> 00:45:09,860
We do not want to get involved into this kind of a thing at all,

722
00:45:09,940 --> 00:45:12,860
that we have broken any family or anything.

723
00:45:12,940 --> 00:45:14,880
If you cannot carry on with a wife,

724
00:45:14,960 --> 00:45:19,160
not that Sahaja Yoga should not be an excuse because you can not carry on with her!

725
00:45:19,240 --> 00:45:23,080
You should have this thing, go out of Sahaja Yoga,

726
00:45:23,160 --> 00:45:25,620
do what you like with your wife, finish it off once

727
00:45:25,700 --> 00:45:27,580
for all, and you should tell her,

728
00:45:27,660 --> 00:45:31,860
“I’m no more a sahaja yogi.” Get it out, and then come to Sahaja Yoga.

729
00:45:31,940 --> 00:45:36,000
But by coming to Sahaja Yoga you’ll be really troubling Me too much.

730
00:45:36,080 --> 00:45:38,220
So I have to make a humble request to you,

731
00:45:38,300 --> 00:45:41,540
that if you have any a such problem don’t come.

732
00:45:42,020 --> 00:45:50,000
Do not allow any child who is younger than a proper age,

733
00:45:50,080 --> 00:45:53,560
sixteen years, to be kept in

734
00:45:54,000 --> 00:45:59,466
the ashram without taking a full permission, written permission, from the parents.

735
00:46:00,040 --> 00:46:05,900
Or a wife who has made problems with the husband, should not be allowed to

736
00:46:05,980 --> 00:46:10,340
come and stay in the ashram with the children unless and until it is resolved.

737
00:46:10,420 --> 00:46:13,686
We are not responsible for all kinds of problems.

738
00:46:14,824 --> 00:46:20,090
Then people who are sick or mentally deranged should not be kept in the ashram.

739
00:46:20,170 --> 00:46:26,560
That is also quite a sympathetic attitude of so many sahaja yogis.

740
00:46:26,640 --> 00:46:29,090
Ashram is for the best people, not for the lunatics.

741
00:46:29,284 --> 00:46:32,550
So please do not get such people who are no good.

742
00:46:32,630 --> 00:46:37,270
We do not want such people to come in the ashram who are going to

743
00:46:37,350 --> 00:46:44,350
ruin the reputation of ashram, so also that you have to establish…

744
00:46:44,430 --> 00:46:49,740
So coming to the relationship of Vishnumaya,

745
00:46:49,820 --> 00:46:54,110
is that Vishnumaya is the One Who is the sister, sister of Shri Krishna.

746
00:46:54,620 --> 00:47:00,580
She’s the One Who announced the coming of Shri Krishna.

747
00:47:01,360 --> 00:47:06,200
She’s the One Who sacrificed Her life to save Shri Krishna’s life.

748
00:47:06,280 --> 00:47:09,260
Vishnumaya is the One which surrounds Shri Krishna,

749
00:47:09,340 --> 00:47:12,300
and She was born as Draupadi who, you

750
00:47:12,380 --> 00:47:16,560
know, was later on humiliated by Duryodhana,

751
00:47:16,640 --> 00:47:19,480
and it was Shri Krishna Who came and helped Her.

752
00:47:19,560 --> 00:47:23,180
So it’s a very sweet relationship of purity, of help,

753
00:47:23,260 --> 00:47:30,380
a very delicate relationship is to be maintained of a brother and a sister.

754
00:47:30,807 --> 00:47:33,540
And that is a special relationship today.

755
00:47:33,620 --> 00:47:39,120
Those who want to tie the Rakhis to a sister should tie today before Me,

756
00:47:39,200 --> 00:47:40,360
it will be a good idea.

757
00:47:40,440 --> 00:47:43,780
It is a greater relationship than any other relationship.

758
00:47:43,860 --> 00:47:49,300
Because here somebody’s your own sister, is all right, but if she’s not

759
00:47:49,380 --> 00:47:53,520
your own sister you should know that you all are born of one Mother.

760
00:47:53,600 --> 00:47:56,560
So the brother and sister relationship should be all right.

761
00:47:56,640 --> 00:48:01,525
In that also one should not have preferences – because some would

762
00:48:01,605 --> 00:48:10,120
like to have a rich sister, or some sort of a nonsense like that.

763
00:48:10,464 --> 00:48:15,530
Or somebody would like to have the most miserable one, this is all the mind.

764
00:48:15,610 --> 00:48:21,230
But a relationship with a person with whom you would like to be happy,

765
00:48:21,310 --> 00:48:25,576
And if there is anybody left out, you should not try to do that.

766
00:48:25,910 --> 00:48:28,450
So anybody who is listening,

767
00:48:28,590 --> 00:48:34,930
I would say that – best thing would be to have your lucky dips I think,

768
00:48:35,010 --> 00:48:38,770
for people, something like that could be done so

769
00:48:38,850 --> 00:48:43,330
that they choose their sisters and tie the things.

770
00:48:43,410 --> 00:48:44,530
Which ever way you like you choose it.

771
00:48:44,610 --> 00:48:48,810
But I have got some nice rakhis for you, that should be done today.

772
00:48:48,890 --> 00:48:50,556
And I will be very happy.

773
00:48:50,700 --> 00:48:56,000
And then we’ll do this little havana for the Vishnumaya.

774
00:48:57,000 --> 00:48:59,000
May God bless you.

